<plot>Tyrannical Turkish grandpa Dede forces lovely Alim to take revenge for his father's death and to kill the Greek Korda next door. But Alim wants to run his vegetable store in peace and is longing for his old friendship to his best former friend Korda. The family store is at stake because Dede wants to hand it over to crazy cousin Sultan in case Alim cannot kill Korda and keep up the pride.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?030222</url></doc>
